## 📌 Quick Tips

- **Start Blender today** — just open it and break things. That's how everyone learns.
- **Your first 10 models will look rough.** That's normal and expected.
- **Document your work** — screenshot everything. Your portfolio starts now.
- **Come to sessions consistently** — each one builds on the last.
- **Ask questions in the group chat** — no question is too basic.

